<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/220681-did-not-realize-how-spirtual-this-would">Did not realize how spirtual this would be. Might have to get a copy to reread whenever....in whole or in pieces parts. Glad to see I am reading these three (Gilead, Home and then Lila in the right order). Now for the question....Where does Housekeeping fit in the picture?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_220681'><a id="like_count_community_question_220681" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/220681?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F68210.Gilead">like</a></span>

</li>
